'''塞拉利昂利昂'''是[[塞拉利昂|塞拉利昂]]的流通貨幣。輔幣單位為分，1利昂=100分。[[ISO_4217|貨幣編號]]'''SLL'''。 

== 历史 ==
利昂自1964年8月4日在塞拉利昂启用，用以替代英属西非磅，兑换比率为1镑兑2利昂。<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Linzmayer | first1 = Owen | title = The Banknote Book | chapter = Sierra Leone | publisher = www.BanknoteNews.com | year = 2012 | location = San Francisco, CA | url = http://www.banknotebook.com | access-date = 2020-10-05 | archive-date = 2012-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120829063428/http://www.banknotebook.com/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

